            "stanza_text": "Si tout mon sang fuit de mon cœur,\nJe veux que, sous ton pied vainqueur,\nEn tombe la dernière goutte !\n— Mon âme errante y sera toute."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Des roses rouges en naîtront",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Qui vers ta bouche élèveront,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Comme des lèvres enflammées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mes blessures jamais fermées.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
